1
00:00:00,513 --> 00:00:02,159
(Episode 2: Mom, Now I Realize)

2
00:00:02,160 --> 00:00:03,333
Doesn't Yu Jun like rice crackers?

3
00:00:04,033 --> 00:00:05,633
Yu Jun, do you want some rice crackers?

4
00:00:06,266 --> 00:00:07,333
Look at Uncle YEONJUN.

5
00:00:07,333 --> 00:00:08,766
(Rice crackers?)

6
00:00:08,766 --> 00:00:11,800
Rice cracker.

7
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:12,866
(Yu Jun's snack time)

8
00:00:13,833 --> 00:00:16,333
(I love rice crackers.)

9
00:00:16,333 --> 00:00:17,533
- He loves it.
- He's cute.

10
00:00:17,533 --> 00:00:18,366
(Leaving)

11
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:19,766
Hey, I gave you a rice cracker.

12
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:21,866
He's cute.
Rice cracker?

13
00:00:22,700 --> 00:00:24,133
(Asking for attention again)

14
00:00:24,133 --> 00:00:25,266
Hug me, then.

15
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,000
Hug me.

16
00:00:27,793 --> 00:00:28,630
Rice cracker?

17
00:00:28,631 --> 00:00:29,800
(I won't give up.)

18
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:31,566
- Give me a hug.
- He's just holding out his hand.

19
00:00:33,433 --> 00:00:34,466
You should give me a hug.

20
00:00:34,466 --> 00:00:36,000
(Thank you for the snack.)

21
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,133
Hey.

22
00:00:37,133 --> 00:00:38,866
YEONJUN has a good character.

23
00:00:39,433 --> 00:00:40,266
Yu Jun.

24
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:42,033
(I, YEONJUN, don't give up.)

25
00:00:42,033 --> 00:00:42,833
He's coming.

26
00:00:42,833 --> 00:00:43,966
Why don't you look at me?

27
00:00:44,433 --> 00:00:45,565
I was right in front of him,

28
00:00:45,566 --> 00:00:47,466
- but he didn't look at me.
- He just passed by.

29
00:00:47,466 --> 00:00:50,300
(In the meantime,
TAEHYUN is preparing strawberries.)

30
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:52,232
- Do you want to eat it?
- Finally, you see me.

31
00:00:52,233 --> 00:00:55,700
(YEONJUN finally got his attention
with strawberry chips.)

32
00:00:56,266 --> 00:00:58,266
Here. I crushed it.

33
00:00:58,266 --> 00:01:00,366
(The strawberry plane is landing.)

34
00:01:00,366 --> 00:01:02,666
(And it's off the route:
I don't want that.)

35
00:01:02,666 --> 00:01:03,966
(Embarrassed)

36
00:01:03,966 --> 00:01:06,800
(Recalculating route)

37
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:08,766
You're looking outside.

38
00:01:09,300 --> 00:01:10,633
Do you want to go outside?

39
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:15,166
- What's in there?
- Yu Jun's clothes for going out.

40
00:01:15,166 --> 00:01:17,033
- We should go out now.
- Yes.

41
00:01:17,166 --> 00:01:19,166
- Is it his day clothes?
- Yes.

42
00:01:20,133 --> 00:01:21,033
It's cute.

43
00:01:21,034 --> 00:01:22,366
(It's way smaller than expected.)

44
00:01:22,366 --> 00:01:24,566
Who feels confident dressing him?

45
00:01:24,566 --> 00:01:25,700
I want to try.

46
00:01:25,700 --> 00:01:27,600
Since that gives me another chance
to hold him.

47
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:30,533
- Do you want to go out?
- Yu Jun, are you ready?

48
00:01:30,533 --> 00:01:31,666
Shall we go out?

49
00:01:31,666 --> 00:01:33,133
Okay. Let's get started, Yu Jun.

50
00:01:33,866 --> 00:01:34,733
Are you ready?

51
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:36,866
(Let me go!)

52
00:01:36,866 --> 00:01:38,733
I'm sorry!

53
00:01:38,733 --> 00:01:41,000
- We should clap.
- Don't say sorry.

54
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,166
Yu Jun, you're okay!

55
00:01:43,166 --> 00:01:45,366
(Yu Jun missed the right time to cry.)

56
00:01:46,433 --> 00:01:48,500
(Congratulations on being fine
after falling!)

57
00:01:48,500 --> 00:01:49,933
Yu Jun!

58
00:01:49,933 --> 00:01:51,100
I give up.

59
00:01:51,700 --> 00:01:52,866
You haven't even tried.

60
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:54,500
I'm scared. I give up.

61
00:01:54,933 --> 00:01:56,900
I'm worried I might make him cry.

62
00:01:56,900 --> 00:01:59,333
- You should undress him first.
- Okay.

63
00:01:59,333 --> 00:02:00,366
What is this?

64
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:02,000
There are buttons on the bottom too.

65
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,666
Let's unbutton it.

66
00:02:03,666 --> 00:02:07,033
(It's going smoothly,
so I should move fast.)

67
00:02:07,033 --> 00:02:09,000
(Buttons undone!)

68
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,633
Good! Here we go, Yu Jun.

69
00:02:10,633 --> 00:02:12,566
How cute. He's so soft.

70
00:02:13,333 --> 00:02:14,466
What do I do? He's adorable.

71
00:02:14,766 --> 00:02:15,633
(Leave me alone!)

72
00:02:15,633 --> 00:02:17,300
Okay. He doesn't want me to touch him.

73
00:02:17,300 --> 00:02:19,766
- Okay, Yu Jun.
- Yu Jun, arms up!

74
00:02:19,766 --> 00:02:21,633
Arms up.

75
00:02:22,166 --> 00:02:23,600
- Yu Jun, arms up.
- Arms up.

76
00:02:24,233 --> 00:02:26,433
- Arms up.
- He's copying you.

77
00:02:27,166 --> 00:02:28,900
Yu Jun, I'm here.

78
00:02:29,466 --> 00:02:30,300
Uncle is...

79
00:02:30,933 --> 00:02:32,100
You don't like it?

80
00:02:32,100 --> 00:02:35,566
(Distracting Yu Jun by singing)

81
00:02:35,566 --> 00:02:37,300
I'm sorry.

82
00:02:38,333 --> 00:02:41,166
There you go.

83
00:02:41,166 --> 00:02:42,766
- Let's take his arms out first.
- There you go.

84
00:02:42,766 --> 00:02:43,800
Take his arms out first.

85
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,366
There you go. Good job!

86
00:02:45,366 --> 00:02:47,800
Good job, Yu Jun!

87
00:02:48,633 --> 00:02:50,433
Yu Jun, let's get dressed.

88
00:02:50,433 --> 00:02:52,033
You must be shy.

89
00:02:52,033 --> 00:02:53,400
- Well done.
- I'm sorry.

90
00:02:53,566 --> 00:02:54,933
Yu Jun, good job.

91
00:02:54,933 --> 00:02:56,233
- So sorry.
- Great job.

92
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:59,800
(Angry)

93
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,233
- Good.
- You don't like it.

94
00:03:01,233 --> 00:03:04,733
- I'm so sorry!
- Yu Jun hates it.

95
00:03:04,733 --> 00:03:05,891
- Let me hold you up for a second.
- Good boy.

96
00:03:05,892 --> 00:03:07,098
(Finally got the T-shirt on)

97
00:03:07,866 --> 00:03:08,997
- Good boy!
- Good job.

98
00:03:08,998 --> 00:03:10,532
(Last step: Overall pants)

99
00:03:10,533 --> 00:03:12,333
- Power Ranger, transform!
- All right.

100
00:03:12,866 --> 00:03:14,033
Overalls!

101
00:03:14,033 --> 00:03:16,833
He's crying, but he's not resisting.

102
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:18,900
He's crying, but he's going along with it.

103
00:03:20,333 --> 00:03:22,433
- My goodness.
- Well done.

104
00:03:22,433 --> 00:03:24,566
(Did they manage to put his overalls on?)

105
00:03:24,566 --> 00:03:26,333
Yu Jun, you've got a strong voice.

106
00:03:29,066 --> 00:03:29,900
Yu Jun.

107
00:03:30,300 --> 00:03:32,766
- They say it's inside out.
- It's inside out.

108
00:03:33,233 --> 00:03:35,300
- How did we put this inside out?
- Let me see.

109
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,366
Lift him again.

110
00:03:37,700 --> 00:03:38,766
- Here we go.
- Yu Jun.

111
00:03:38,766 --> 00:03:39,900
- In 1, 2, 3.
- In 1, 2, 3.

112
00:03:39,900 --> 00:03:41,333
(A chaotic Parenting Diary)

113
00:03:41,333 --> 00:03:44,200
Let's do the airplane!

114
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,766
- It's so much fun!
- It's amazing.

115
00:03:45,766 --> 00:03:46,866
Is this inside out?

116
00:03:48,166 --> 00:03:49,700
Is the top inside out?

117
00:03:50,066 --> 00:03:51,500
(Shocked)

118
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:53,633
- Is this backward?
- Is the top inside out?

119
00:03:53,633 --> 00:03:54,933
Shouldn't we just give up on the top?

120
00:03:54,933 --> 00:03:56,833
- You hate it.
- I'm sorry.

121
00:03:56,833 --> 00:03:58,333
(Their biggest crisis since debut)

122
00:03:58,333 --> 00:04:00,333
- Uncle's sorry.
- Bring me a snack.

123
00:04:02,533 --> 00:04:03,833
Done. Yu Jun, you're done.

124
00:04:04,633 --> 00:04:05,721
He doesn't want your hands on him.

125
00:04:07,666 --> 00:04:09,900
(Comforting him with rice crackers)

126
00:04:10,433 --> 00:04:12,600
(Crying)

127
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:14,033
(Crying is one thing,
and a snack is another.)

128
00:04:14,033 --> 00:04:15,466
- He can't resist.
- You know it's good.

129
00:04:15,466 --> 00:04:17,500
You're upset, but you still eat anyway.

130
00:04:18,933 --> 00:04:19,933
Done!

131
00:04:19,933 --> 00:04:22,466
- Yu Jun, we're done.
- Done.

132
00:04:22,466 --> 00:04:23,866
Shall we go out now?

133
00:04:24,933 --> 00:04:26,933
He's blowing bubbles out of his nose.

134
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:28,800
He's upset.

135
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,500
Guys, we should pack his bag.

136
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:32,533
We've always had someone dress us,

137
00:04:32,533 --> 00:04:35,000
- we've never dressed anyone before.
- I wouldn't like it...

138
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,466
if five stylists tried to dress me.

139
00:04:37,466 --> 00:04:39,733
Right. Forcefully.

140
00:04:39,733 --> 00:04:40,895
Mom.

141
00:04:40,896 --> 00:04:42,332
(Yu Jun is crying, and so is YEONJUN.)

142
00:04:42,333 --> 00:04:43,500
Mom.

143
00:04:44,633 --> 00:04:45,933
Mom!

144
00:04:45,933 --> 00:04:47,733
(I miss you, Mom.)

145
00:04:47,733 --> 00:04:49,300
Yu Jun, you look so good!

146
00:04:49,566 --> 00:04:51,100
(Now that he's calm,
he's ready to go out.)

147
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:53,066
Yu Jun is handsome, by the way.

148
00:04:53,966 --> 00:04:54,900
He's so cute.

149
00:04:55,233 --> 00:04:56,033
Shall we get going?

150
00:04:56,633 --> 00:04:57,933
Let's go, Yu Jun.

151
00:04:58,266 --> 00:04:59,166
Let's take rice crackers.

152
00:04:59,166 --> 00:05:00,233
Let's go outside.

153
00:05:00,233 --> 00:05:02,100
Shall we go, Yu Jun?

154
00:05:02,100 --> 00:05:03,333
Let me put your shoes on for you.

155
00:05:06,366 --> 00:05:07,700
Good boy.

156
00:05:07,700 --> 00:05:08,766
They're so small.

157
00:05:09,066 --> 00:05:11,333
(Amazed by the small shoes)

158
00:05:11,333 --> 00:05:12,866
- If we go outside, he'll follow us.
- Shall we go?

159
00:05:13,266 --> 00:05:14,833
- I want to go out.
- Which ones are mine?

160
00:05:14,833 --> 00:05:15,700
Let's go.

161
00:05:15,700 --> 00:05:21,266
(Their official outing, 4:30 p.m.)

162
00:05:22,166 --> 00:05:23,933
(Yu Jun and TOMORROW X TOGETHER
came to a nearby playground.)

163
00:05:23,933 --> 00:05:24,733
Let's go.

164
00:05:27,033 --> 00:05:28,633
Yu Jun, there's a train here.

165
00:05:28,966 --> 00:05:30,766
- A train.
- A train.

166
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,733
- It's been a while.
- A train is fast.

167
00:05:33,733 --> 00:05:34,500
What?

168
00:05:34,733 --> 00:05:36,433
What's next? A plane is fast.

169
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,366
(BEOMGYU's camera)

170
00:05:38,366 --> 00:05:40,100
- He saw the stairs.
- He saw the stairs.

171
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:41,000
Hold him.

172
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:43,433
Okay, Yu Jun!

173
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:44,700
Let's go.

174
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:47,966
(Yu Jun goes up the stairs
with BEOMGYU's help.)

175
00:05:47,966 --> 00:05:49,100
He's doing good.

176
00:05:49,266 --> 00:05:50,166
He's doing a good job.

177
00:05:50,166 --> 00:05:51,800
Actually, I'm lifting him a little.

178
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,866
- He's a little upset.
- Good job.

179
00:05:53,866 --> 00:05:55,333
He loves the stairs.

180
00:05:55,633 --> 00:05:58,200
(Childcare Diary Tip: He loves stairs.)

181
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,700
Good boy.

182
00:05:59,700 --> 00:06:01,166
He loves stairs.

183
00:06:01,166 --> 00:06:02,033
Yu Jun!

184
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:03,400
There you go.

185
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,566
Go down that slide over there.

186
00:06:04,566 --> 00:06:05,600
Okay.

187
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,833
Yes. Go down the slide with him.

188
00:06:06,833 --> 00:06:08,600
Hold him on your lap
and slide down together.

189
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,900
I hear something from there.

190
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:10,833
Yu Jun, what's that?

191
00:06:10,833 --> 00:06:12,933
- Yu Jun.
- What's that?

192
00:06:14,866 --> 00:06:15,800
Shall we go down?

193
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,500
Shall we go, Yu Jun?

194
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:19,333
(The slide is too small for HUENINGKAI.)

195
00:06:19,333 --> 00:06:20,300
Shall we go?

196
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:22,233
Make his butt touch the slide...

197
00:06:22,233 --> 00:06:23,433
so he can feel the ride too.

198
00:06:23,833 --> 00:06:24,900
It's so narrow.

199
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:25,900
- Shall we go?
- Here we go.

200
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:27,633
Let's go!

201
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:30,666
All right!

202
00:06:30,666 --> 00:06:32,266
It's so much fun.

203
00:06:32,266 --> 00:06:34,266
- One more time?
- Yu Jun is happy.

204
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:37,500
- Yu Jun is sliding.
- You are so brave!

205
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:40,133
- Good job.
- One more time?

206
00:06:40,133 --> 00:06:41,100
One more time!

207
00:06:41,433 --> 00:06:43,366
It was fun.

208
00:06:43,366 --> 00:06:45,833
Yu Jun, come with YEONJUN, all right?

209
00:06:47,633 --> 00:06:48,800
(Climbing the stairs while babbling)

210
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,600
Okay. There you go.

211
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,766
He's doing great.

212
00:06:51,766 --> 00:06:53,800
- Okay!
- Yes!

213
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:56,300
- He'd love long escalators.
- Good job!

214
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:59,233
Nice! Yes!

215
00:06:59,866 --> 00:07:02,600
Yu Jun and YEONJUN's collaboration.
Let's go.

216
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,366
(Let's go already.)

217
00:07:05,758 --> 00:07:07,199
(Monster voice to amuse Yu Jun)

218
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,600
I'm sorry.

219
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,200
(Roaring)

220
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:11,600
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

221
00:07:13,366 --> 00:07:16,100
(Rice Cracker Uncle is waiting for him
down the slide.)

222
00:07:16,100 --> 00:07:16,900
Cracker rice.
Is this a cracker rice?

223
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,366
- A rice cracker.
- A rice cracker.

224
00:07:20,100 --> 00:07:21,066
Rice cracker.

225
00:07:21,633 --> 00:07:23,433
There you go. He loves it.

226
00:07:23,433 --> 00:07:24,900
Don't come.

227
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:26,400
Don't come yet.

228
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:30,033
- Don't come!
- I got him.

229
00:07:30,033 --> 00:07:31,266
- Here I come.
- Let's get out.

230
00:07:32,033 --> 00:07:33,633
- What's with them?
- Here I go.

231
00:07:37,666 --> 00:07:38,500
This is fun.

232
00:07:39,866 --> 00:07:41,200
I'm going to go first.

233
00:07:42,033 --> 00:07:44,566
- He's going up the stairs.
- He's better than before.

234
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,566
Nice job.

235
00:07:46,566 --> 00:07:47,966
He got interested.

236
00:07:47,966 --> 00:07:49,166
- Be careful.
- Do you want to ride that?

237
00:07:49,166 --> 00:07:50,100
Do you want to try that?

238
00:07:50,100 --> 00:07:51,633
- He wants to ride it.
- Do you want to go on that?

239
00:07:51,933 --> 00:07:53,766
After seeing us go on it,
he wants to try it too.

240
00:07:54,366 --> 00:07:55,766
Then let's catch him.

241
00:07:55,766 --> 00:07:58,333
- TAEHYUN, catch him.
- A little lower.

242
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:03,266
(That was fun.)

243
00:08:03,266 --> 00:08:04,700
What's up, baby?

244
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:05,500
Do you want to go again?

245
00:08:06,433 --> 00:08:07,966
- One more time.
- One more time.

246
00:08:07,966 --> 00:08:09,000
Yu Jun, let's go?

247
00:08:09,733 --> 00:08:10,766
Do you want to ride it with me?

248
00:08:10,766 --> 00:08:11,966
Yu Jun.

249
00:08:11,966 --> 00:08:13,266
- Be careful.
- I kept bumping my head.

250
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,366
Do you want to ride it with him?

251
00:08:16,900 --> 00:08:18,200
His nose is running.

252
00:08:18,766 --> 00:08:19,600
Shall we go, Yu Jun?

253
00:08:20,466 --> 00:08:21,766
In 1, 2, 3.

254
00:08:21,766 --> 00:08:24,800
(Sliding)

255
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,566
Good job.

256
00:08:27,666 --> 00:08:28,633
(I like this.)
One more time.

257
00:08:29,433 --> 00:08:30,466
- One more time?
- He's turning around.

258
00:08:30,466 --> 00:08:31,300
Are you turning around?

259
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:33,733
(I can get up by myself.)

260
00:08:33,733 --> 00:08:35,566
There you go.
You need to learn to get up on your own.

261
00:08:35,566 --> 00:08:36,733
- Well done!
- There you go!

262
00:08:36,733 --> 00:08:38,466
(He encourages Yu Jun to be independent.)

263
00:08:38,700 --> 00:08:42,166
(Sliding down)

264
00:08:42,166 --> 00:08:44,366
(I love it.)

265
00:08:44,366 --> 00:08:45,200
He wants you to do it again.

266
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,666
He keeps looking at you.

267
00:08:46,666 --> 00:08:49,866
(That's how the endless sliding began.)

268
00:08:52,166 --> 00:08:53,300
He's happy.

269
00:08:54,966 --> 00:09:01,033
(Childcare Diary Tip:
Don't play passively. Use your body.)

270
00:09:01,033 --> 00:09:03,200
(Clapping together)

271
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,500
(Sliding)

272
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,633
Yes!

273
00:09:07,633 --> 00:09:08,800
(One more time!)

274
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:10,000
One more time.

275
00:09:10,933 --> 00:09:14,066
(His reaction is getting better
and better.)

276
00:09:14,066 --> 00:09:15,566
He's having so much fun.

277
00:09:15,566 --> 00:09:17,766
- As long as you're happy, we're happy.
- We are.

278
00:09:18,716 --> 00:09:19,692
This is the time.

279
00:09:19,866 --> 00:09:21,233
- Our secret weapon.
- Here.

280
00:09:21,233 --> 00:09:22,966
- Who wants to blow?
- Yu Jun, look at that?

281
00:09:26,066 --> 00:09:27,166
What could that be?

282
00:09:28,133 --> 00:09:29,566
- Isn't that fascinating?
- It's amazing!

283
00:09:31,033 --> 00:09:32,433
I knew it. I've never met...

284
00:09:32,433 --> 00:09:35,133
- a kid who doesn't like it.
- We should get this.

285
00:09:35,133 --> 00:09:36,600
- It's so pretty.
- Directors, please get this.

286
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,466
It's like a magazine photoshoot.

287
00:09:37,466 --> 00:09:39,500
(BEOMGYU also films Yu Jun.)

288
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,533
- Hey, you're good at this.
- He loves it.

289
00:09:41,533 --> 00:09:42,333
He's cute.

290
00:09:44,366 --> 00:09:47,100
(Mesmerized)

291
00:09:47,533 --> 00:09:48,600
That's adorable.

292
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,166
- He's so cute.
- Is it fascinating?

293
00:09:51,166 --> 00:09:52,133
It's amazing.

294
00:09:52,133 --> 00:09:54,266
(YEONJUN also films him.)

295
00:09:54,266 --> 00:09:55,633
- Blow the bubbles lower.
- Right.

296
00:09:55,633 --> 00:09:56,866
- He's so cute.
- Toward the ground.

297
00:09:56,866 --> 00:09:59,066
(YEONJUN's phone camera)

298
00:09:59,614 --> 00:10:01,014
Yu Jun, let me film you closely.

299
00:10:01,835 --> 00:10:03,836
This is like "Fairy of Shampoo!"

300
00:10:05,005 --> 00:10:05,838
This is a fan cam of Yu Jun.

301
00:10:06,473 --> 00:10:07,973
The wind is blowing this way.

302
00:10:07,974 --> 00:10:10,309
(A fan cam of his adorable behind)

303
00:10:11,111 --> 00:10:12,478
It's like we're kids again.

304
00:10:14,581 --> 00:10:16,549
He's laughing. He's not crying.

305
00:10:18,485 --> 00:10:19,684
Oh, gosh!

306
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,952
My back.

307
00:10:21,154 --> 00:10:22,287
This is our first walk.

308
00:10:22,288 --> 00:10:24,156
Let's take a photo to celebrate it.

309
00:10:24,157 --> 00:10:25,257
A photo.

310
00:10:25,258 --> 00:10:27,026
(A family photo to celebrate
their first outing)

311
00:10:27,027 --> 00:10:27,860
Okay!

312
00:10:28,194 --> 00:10:30,195
We'll take a video and take screenshots.

313
00:10:30,196 --> 00:10:31,830
- Okay.
- Let's all pose.

314
00:10:31,831 --> 00:10:32,631
Everyone's in the frame.
That looks fun!

315
00:10:33,599 --> 00:10:34,866
Let's go up, Yu Jun.

316
00:10:35,701 --> 00:10:36,870
Let's have two on each side.

317
00:10:37,070 --> 00:10:37,936
Look at that!

318
00:10:38,538 --> 00:10:40,305
- Look over there!
- Ready?

319
00:10:41,074 --> 00:10:41,840
Blow the bubbles.

320
00:10:41,941 --> 00:10:43,141
In 1, 2, 3.

321
00:10:44,611 --> 00:10:45,442
Slide down.

322
00:10:45,578 --> 00:10:46,811
Let's take one of us going down.

323
00:10:46,812 --> 00:10:48,547
Okay, in 1, 2, 3.

324
00:10:48,548 --> 00:10:49,548
Down you go!

325
00:10:49,549 --> 00:10:51,149
(Directed, filmed, and props by TAEHYUN)

326
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,817
(Effects by HUENINGKAI)

327
00:10:52,818 --> 00:10:53,518
Smile!

328
00:10:53,953 --> 00:10:54,986
You look so happy!

329
00:10:55,355 --> 00:10:57,289
- You're so happy.
- My gosh!

330
00:10:57,290 --> 00:10:58,223
We definitely got a good shot.

331
00:10:58,224 --> 00:11:01,761
(That's how we got this poster.)

332
00:11:03,331 --> 00:11:06,131
Yu Jun, here I come!

333
00:11:06,866 --> 00:11:07,732
You'll get hurt.

334
00:11:07,734 --> 00:11:08,834
Run that way.

335
00:11:09,769 --> 00:11:10,602
Do you like running?

336
00:11:10,805 --> 00:11:12,004
Do you want to run too?

337
00:11:12,939 --> 00:11:13,806
Do you want to run?

338
00:11:14,908 --> 00:11:15,909
Oh, goodness.

339
00:11:16,076 --> 00:11:17,843
- Are you ready to run?
- Here I come!

340
00:11:17,944 --> 00:11:19,177
(Running)

341
00:11:19,178 --> 00:11:20,012
He's so cute.

342
00:11:20,313 --> 00:11:21,947
How can he run with such tiny legs?

343
00:11:21,948 --> 00:11:23,515
(Being overly enthusiastic
to keep up with Yu Jun)

344
00:11:23,516 --> 00:11:25,117
Yu Jun, party people!

345
00:11:26,119 --> 00:11:26,984
Yu Jun!

346
00:11:27,654 --> 00:11:29,021
- Yu Jun!
- This is so embarrassing.

347
00:11:29,656 --> 00:11:31,523
(But he's your teammate.)

348
00:11:31,524 --> 00:11:32,357
Yu Jun.

349
00:11:32,427 --> 00:11:33,926
(Look at me!)

350
00:11:35,495 --> 00:11:36,562
He's not even remotely interested.

351
00:11:38,464 --> 00:11:40,565
(Yu Jun is suddenly getting fussy.)

352
00:11:40,566 --> 00:11:41,833
It's okay!

353
00:11:41,834 --> 00:11:42,867
Did he pee?

354
00:11:42,868 --> 00:11:43,768
- What?
- What?

355
00:11:44,204 --> 00:11:44,970
Did he pee?

356
00:11:45,138 --> 00:11:46,439
I think he peed.

357
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,973
Why? Does his diaper smell?

358
00:11:47,974 --> 00:11:49,742
- No.
- It's just that he's crying.

359
00:11:49,743 --> 00:11:53,145
(I had a good time.)

360
00:11:53,146 --> 00:11:53,979
We're home!

361
00:11:54,180 --> 00:11:55,281
- We're home!
- So cute.

362
00:11:55,482 --> 00:11:56,715
What's that?

363
00:11:56,984 --> 00:11:58,584
This is so exciting!

364
00:11:58,585 --> 00:11:59,885
It's time to change his diaper.

365
00:11:59,886 --> 00:12:01,220
Good boy!

366
00:12:01,221 --> 00:12:04,089
- It's time to get changed!
- Good boy!

367
00:12:04,090 --> 00:12:07,292
- Good boy!
- Good boy!

368
00:12:07,293 --> 00:12:09,395
(Getting ready)

369
00:12:09,396 --> 00:12:10,396
(So distracted)

370
00:12:10,397 --> 00:12:12,131
- Yu Jun!
- Good boy!

371
00:12:12,132 --> 00:12:13,098
Let's go!

372
00:12:13,099 --> 00:12:14,733
(Dividing roles after the initial failure)

373
00:12:14,734 --> 00:12:15,601
Good boy!

374
00:12:15,602 --> 00:12:17,336
- What's this?
- Good boy!

375
00:12:17,537 --> 00:12:18,971
- Good boy!
- How do we do this?

376
00:12:19,272 --> 00:12:20,138
Where are the diapers?
Let's get the pants first.

377
00:12:21,207 --> 00:12:23,575
- Do we need to change his diaper?
- Yes, we do.

378
00:12:23,576 --> 00:12:24,442
He peed.

379
00:12:24,443 --> 00:12:25,944
Good boy!

380
00:12:25,945 --> 00:12:27,879
(Moving efficiently
and making noises nonstop)

381
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:28,847
What's that?

382
00:12:29,082 --> 00:12:31,216
What's this, Yu Jun?

383
00:12:31,518 --> 00:12:32,485
Look!

384
00:12:32,486 --> 00:12:34,120
- Distract him.
- What's this?

385
00:12:34,121 --> 00:12:35,121
What is this?

386
00:12:35,122 --> 00:12:36,589
- Can you tell me?
- Good boy!

387
00:12:36,590 --> 00:12:38,924
(Let's take a break from captioning.)

388
00:12:38,925 --> 00:12:40,292
What's this?

389
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:41,894
- It's a button!
- How do you do it?

390
00:12:42,028 --> 00:12:43,228
- How does this work?
- Good boy!

391
00:12:43,229 --> 00:12:44,229
Yu Jun, can you show me?

392
00:12:44,230 --> 00:12:45,230
Is this the button?

393
00:12:45,231 --> 00:12:46,498
That's the power button.

394
00:12:46,499 --> 00:12:47,799
Good boy! You peed so much.

395
00:12:48,034 --> 00:12:49,101
That's so cool!

396
00:12:50,137 --> 00:12:52,270
- This is so cool!
- How cool is that?

397
00:12:52,705 --> 00:12:54,039
It's making funny noises!

398
00:12:55,475 --> 00:12:58,677
(Should I cry or not?)

399
00:12:59,212 --> 00:13:00,546
What is this, Yu Jun?

400
00:13:00,547 --> 00:13:02,147
(It's time to cry.)

401
00:13:02,982 --> 00:13:07,152
(The second disastrous outfit change
has begun.)

402
00:13:07,620 --> 00:13:08,553
Look!

403
00:13:08,554 --> 00:13:11,522
(Facing away from the cameras
to help Yu Jun)

404
00:13:11,523 --> 00:13:13,557
Nice!

405
00:13:13,558 --> 00:13:14,459
We're done!

406
00:13:15,828 --> 00:13:17,962
- Good boy!
- You did it!

407
00:13:17,963 --> 00:13:19,532
(He cried, but the first diaper change was
a success.)

408
00:13:20,132 --> 00:13:21,432
Get me a wet wipe.

409
00:13:21,433 --> 00:13:23,001
Get me a towel.

410
00:13:23,002 --> 00:13:24,102
Look!

411
00:13:24,103 --> 00:13:25,303
Can you raise your arms?

412
00:13:25,304 --> 00:13:26,237
You're the best!

413
00:13:26,238 --> 00:13:27,338
There we go!

414
00:13:28,408 --> 00:13:29,808
You're so brave!

415
00:13:29,809 --> 00:13:31,543
(I don't want to put it on!)

416
00:13:31,544 --> 00:13:32,711
You don't want to wear it?

417
00:13:32,712 --> 00:13:36,315
(ANXIOUS BY TOGETHER)

418
00:13:37,116 --> 00:13:39,050
- There we go!
- Good boy!

419
00:13:39,051 --> 00:13:41,786
- This arm first, then that arm.
- Good boy!

420
00:13:41,787 --> 00:13:44,522
You're such a good boy!

421
00:13:44,523 --> 00:13:46,491
- We're almost done!
- Do you want a plane ride?

422
00:13:47,794 --> 00:13:50,362
(Now is the time! Put his pants on!)

423
00:13:50,363 --> 00:13:51,730
Let's go!

424
00:13:52,232 --> 00:13:53,666
(Stay strong!)

425
00:13:53,667 --> 00:13:54,700
Right on!

426
00:13:56,736 --> 00:13:57,736
There we go!

427
00:13:57,737 --> 00:13:59,504
(The second changing frenzy went
more smoothly than earlier.)

428
00:13:59,505 --> 00:14:01,206
- We're done!
- It's over!

429
00:14:01,341 --> 00:14:03,275
- It's all done.
- We're done!

430
00:14:03,276 --> 00:14:04,910
We're good now!

431
00:14:05,912 --> 00:14:07,513
It's not scary now
that you've done it, right?

432
00:14:09,882 --> 00:14:13,017
(TAEHYUN is in the kitchen
immediately after the outfit change.)

433
00:14:13,018 --> 00:14:14,587
Do you want to play with this?

434
00:14:14,854 --> 00:14:16,654
How do you use this, Yu Jun?

435
00:14:17,656 --> 00:14:19,092
How do you use this?

436
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:21,626
Do you want some milk?

437
00:14:23,896 --> 00:14:25,230
He loves drinking milk!

438
00:14:25,398 --> 00:14:27,366
- He's drinking it up.
- You'll grow so tall!

439
00:14:27,367 --> 00:14:28,834
He's asking for another sip.

440
00:14:29,836 --> 00:14:32,439
- Be careful with the straw.
- We don't want to hurt him.

441
00:14:33,640 --> 00:14:34,873
- Is it good?
- You like it?

442
00:14:34,874 --> 00:14:36,341
Was that good?

443
00:14:36,342 --> 00:14:38,076
He's smiling.

444
00:14:38,077 --> 00:14:39,278
Do you want more?

445
00:14:40,009 --> 00:14:41,280
Don't you feel so fresh?

446
00:14:41,781 --> 00:14:43,749
- High-five!
- He's so happy.

447
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:44,583
Okay.

448
00:14:45,084 --> 00:14:47,886
(Drinking milk
with tears still on his face)

449
00:14:47,887 --> 00:14:48,720
- Is it good?
- Yu Jun.

450
00:14:49,255 --> 00:14:51,257
- Yu Jun.
- It's so good, right?

451
00:14:51,258 --> 00:14:52,156
Yu Jun!

452
00:14:53,726 --> 00:14:54,960
- Yu Jun?
- He wants to finish this first.

453
00:14:54,961 --> 00:14:55,794
YEONJUN?

454
00:14:56,696 --> 00:14:57,596
YEONJUN?

455
00:14:57,797 --> 00:14:59,431
- Yu Jun?
- He loves milk.

456
00:14:59,432 --> 00:15:00,298
YEONJUN?

457
00:15:01,934 --> 00:15:03,735
(That was some good milk!)

458
00:15:03,736 --> 00:15:04,704
He's adorable.

459
00:15:05,238 --> 00:15:07,372
- Don't give him more.
- He finished it.

460
00:15:07,373 --> 00:15:09,274
- We don't have more.
- He finished it.

461
00:15:12,779 --> 00:15:13,645
Who's there?

462
00:15:13,846 --> 00:15:15,113
- The baby chair is here.
- The baby chair.

463
00:15:15,315 --> 00:15:16,982
Hold that up.

464
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:18,350
And put it in here.

465
00:15:18,611 --> 00:15:19,578
Hold on.

466
00:15:19,603 --> 00:15:20,986
(SOOBIN and HUENINGKAI are playing
with Yu Jun.)

467
00:15:20,987 --> 00:15:22,555
Should we see if Yu Jun fits in the chair?

468
00:15:23,323 --> 00:15:24,991
They went in so smoothly.

469
00:15:25,091 --> 00:15:26,225
Except for two.

470
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:28,961
Great job!

471
00:15:29,629 --> 00:15:30,762
Good boy.

472
00:15:31,164 --> 00:15:32,097
Yu Jun!

473
00:15:32,465 --> 00:15:33,932
- Hold on.
- Look here!

474
00:15:33,933 --> 00:15:35,100
What do we do with this part?

475
00:15:35,101 --> 00:15:38,303
(TAEHYUN is alone in the kitchen
making dinner for Yu Jun.)

476
00:15:40,273 --> 00:15:46,111
(Dinner is at 6 p.m.)

477
00:15:46,112 --> 00:15:51,216
("Yu Jun loves eggs. He'll eat anything
with scrambled eggs!")

478
00:15:51,217 --> 00:15:56,755
("Please cool the food
before feeding it to him!")

479
00:15:59,792 --> 00:16:00,692
How do I insert it?

480
00:16:01,260 --> 00:16:02,493
Does it go this way?

481
00:16:03,596 --> 00:16:04,996
This should work.

482
00:16:04,997 --> 00:16:06,464
- Come here.
- I'll take it.

483
00:16:06,465 --> 00:16:08,032
Hooray!

484
00:16:09,235 --> 00:16:10,769
It needs to go in more.

485
00:16:10,770 --> 00:16:12,003
- More?
- Yes.

486
00:16:12,004 --> 00:16:12,869
Food?

487
00:16:13,706 --> 00:16:14,639
Yu Jun, it's your dinner!

488
00:16:16,042 --> 00:16:17,275
It's dinnertime!

489
00:16:18,512 --> 00:16:19,478
Are you ready to eat?

490
00:16:20,146 --> 00:16:21,213
What's with his voice?

491
00:16:22,115 --> 00:16:23,481
Look at that!

492
00:16:23,649 --> 00:16:25,416
- Is it good?
- Is it yummy?

493
00:16:25,618 --> 00:16:26,685
Some eggs?

494
00:16:26,686 --> 00:16:28,386
Let's eat now.

495
00:16:29,555 --> 00:16:31,155
Good boy!

496
00:16:31,156 --> 00:16:33,858
(SOOBIN and TAEHYUN are so happy
to see Yu Jun eat well.)

497
00:16:35,328 --> 00:16:36,429
He's eating better than earlier.

498
00:16:36,628 --> 00:16:37,862
- Yes.
- He must be hungry.

499
00:16:38,432 --> 00:16:39,932
Much hungrier than earlier.

500
00:16:40,233 --> 00:16:41,200
Does he not need water?

501
00:16:41,667 --> 00:16:42,567
Do you want water?

502
00:16:42,735 --> 00:16:44,202
Would you like some water?

503
00:16:44,837 --> 00:16:45,737
Here's your water.

504
00:16:45,738 --> 00:16:48,540
(Such a romantic pose
for feeding water to a baby)

505
00:16:49,108 --> 00:16:49,941
Do you want this?

506
00:16:49,942 --> 00:16:51,176
(I want food now.)

507
00:16:51,177 --> 00:16:53,912
(HUENINGKAI has become Yu Jun's butler.)

508
00:16:53,913 --> 00:16:55,013
Open up!

509
00:16:55,715 --> 00:16:57,516
Good boy! You eat so well.

510
00:17:00,153 --> 00:17:02,588
(A high-five for the chef)

511
00:17:03,022 --> 00:17:05,057
Yes, he knows I cooked for him.

512
00:17:05,457 --> 00:17:06,658
- I'm glad.
- It must be good.

513
00:17:06,659 --> 00:17:07,993
- He likes the food.
- He's back for more.

514
00:17:07,994 --> 00:17:09,027
That's right. I'm the chef!

515
00:17:09,829 --> 00:17:10,863
He must love the food.

516
00:17:10,864 --> 00:17:12,864
So yummy!

517
00:17:13,399 --> 00:17:14,799
Come here, Yu Jun.

518
00:17:15,868 --> 00:17:17,303
Do you want to push that over there?

519
00:17:17,537 --> 00:17:19,071
Let's make a U-turn.

520
00:17:20,506 --> 00:17:22,247
You're kidding me.
There's no way it hasn't even been a day.

521
00:17:23,309 --> 00:17:24,309
This is so much fun!

522
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:26,011
Are you telling me it hasn't been 90 days?

523
00:17:26,879 --> 00:17:28,346
What time is it?

524
00:17:28,347 --> 00:17:29,247
Let's bring it down again.

525
00:17:29,248 --> 00:17:31,348
(An extra slow day)

526
00:17:32,251 --> 00:17:33,918
- Good job.
- We're back!

527
00:17:33,919 --> 00:17:34,752
Come here, Yu Jun.

528
00:17:36,155 --> 00:17:37,222
(YEONJUN is Yu Jun's chair.)

529
00:17:37,223 --> 00:17:38,056
Open up!

530
00:17:38,925 --> 00:17:40,024
Good boy!

531
00:17:40,159 --> 00:17:41,365
Good job.

532
00:17:41,366 --> 00:17:42,494
(The meal tastes good today.)

533
00:17:42,495 --> 00:17:44,996
- Hold on.
- So, this is how it works.

534
00:17:45,832 --> 00:17:47,132
You eat so well!

535
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:49,434
Do you want this?

536
00:17:49,635 --> 00:17:50,468
Gosh.

537
00:17:50,670 --> 00:17:51,971
Something fell.

538
00:17:52,004 --> 00:17:53,572
His taste changed.

539
00:17:53,906 --> 00:17:55,006
You liked eggs earlier.

540
00:17:55,475 --> 00:17:56,408
(The one feeding him)
Open up, Yu Jun.

541
00:17:57,743 --> 00:17:58,910
Open up!

542
00:17:59,212 --> 00:18:00,279
- Come on.
- Here comes the airplane!

543
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:01,046
Open up!

544
00:18:01,314 --> 00:18:03,748
- Open up. Good boy!
- Good boy!

545
00:18:04,717 --> 00:18:06,084
(I love eggs.)

546
00:18:06,085 --> 00:18:07,752
Do you want this?

547
00:18:08,688 --> 00:18:10,121
This is really good, right?

548
00:18:10,657 --> 00:18:12,323
He really loves eggs.

549
00:18:12,526 --> 00:18:13,659
He loves eggs.

550
00:18:13,759 --> 00:18:14,625
One more spoon.

551
00:18:15,127 --> 00:18:16,661
More eggs? Sure!

552
00:18:17,230 --> 00:18:21,300
(The uncles with the bleached hair are
starting to understand Yu Jun.)

553
00:18:22,203 --> 00:18:23,167
(Going more smoothly than lunch)

554
00:18:23,168 --> 00:18:24,804
- Eggs?
- This?

555
00:18:25,338 --> 00:18:26,104
This?

556
00:18:26,539 --> 00:18:28,407
- Do you want my help?
- Look at the back of his head.

557
00:18:30,877 --> 00:18:31,677
(Water!)

558
00:18:31,678 --> 00:18:32,812
- Water?
- Water first.

559
00:18:33,646 --> 00:18:34,479
There we go.

560
00:18:36,082 --> 00:18:37,816
Is it good?

561
00:18:37,817 --> 00:18:38,583
All done!

562
00:18:38,985 --> 00:18:41,553
(Yu Jun's dinner is over.)

563
00:18:41,554 --> 00:18:42,554
That was a great dinner.

564
00:18:42,855 --> 00:18:44,657
- Can you clean up the spills?
- Yes.

565
00:18:45,291 --> 00:18:48,793
(What's the next task
for the rookie babysitters?)

566
00:18:48,794 --> 00:18:50,729
Yu Jun, are you ready to brush your teeth?

567
00:18:50,730 --> 00:18:52,097
(The air is tense in the living room.)

568
00:18:52,098 --> 00:18:54,133
I bet it's one of the hardest tasks.

569
00:18:54,634 --> 00:18:55,901
Brushing his teeth.

570
00:18:55,902 --> 00:18:57,603
Come here, Yu Jun.

571
00:18:58,117 --> 00:18:59,671
Let's have a meet-and-greet.

572
00:18:59,672 --> 00:19:00,504
Okay.

573
00:19:00,505 --> 00:19:02,407
We have to distract him really well,

574
00:19:02,408 --> 00:19:03,875
and we can't hold him too tightly.

575
00:19:03,876 --> 00:19:06,044
- It's harder than changing his diaper.
- And just brush...

576
00:19:06,045 --> 00:19:07,312
the teeth we can see.

577
00:19:07,313 --> 00:19:08,613
His teeth don't need a lot of brushing.

578
00:19:09,982 --> 00:19:10,748
You're so happy!

579
00:19:10,749 --> 00:19:12,450
You see lights in the reflection!

580
00:19:12,451 --> 00:19:13,651
- Yu Jun!
- It's you!

581
00:19:13,652 --> 00:19:14,786
He can see himself.

582
00:19:14,787 --> 00:19:18,323
- That's you!
- Yu Jun, you're in the reflection!

583
00:19:20,092 --> 00:19:21,325
Isn't it so cool?

584
00:19:21,326 --> 00:19:22,795
- Are you trying to escape?
- Yu Jun.

585
00:19:23,229 --> 00:19:24,729
"Let me out!"

586
00:19:24,730 --> 00:19:25,764
(Creeping up on him)

587
00:19:25,765 --> 00:19:26,865
(Is he taking the toothbrush?)

588
00:19:26,866 --> 00:19:27,832
He's taking it!

589
00:19:27,833 --> 00:19:29,000
(I fooled you!)

590
00:19:29,001 --> 00:19:29,901
He felt something.

591
00:19:29,902 --> 00:19:31,770
Let him out.

592
00:19:31,771 --> 00:19:32,837
We're trapping him.

593
00:19:32,838 --> 00:19:34,639
Yu Jun, not there!

594
00:19:34,774 --> 00:19:36,508
(Screaming in pain)

595
00:19:36,509 --> 00:19:37,642
- Okay.
- Yu Jun!

596
00:19:38,878 --> 00:19:39,911
Okay, we'll let you go.

597
00:19:41,113 --> 00:19:42,980
Yu Jun doesn't like being trapped.

598
00:19:42,981 --> 00:19:44,248
Please, Yu Jun!

599
00:19:45,485 --> 00:19:48,820
(A rare sight of TOMORROW X TOGETHER
chasing one person)

600
00:19:48,821 --> 00:19:49,688
Oh, sorry!

601
00:19:50,423 --> 00:19:51,957
There you are!

602
00:19:51,958 --> 00:19:53,892
(He's surrounded again after escaping.)

603
00:19:53,893 --> 00:19:55,261
The vacuum cleaner...

604
00:19:56,696 --> 00:19:59,564
What is this shiny thing?

605
00:20:00,194 --> 00:20:01,894
What's this, Yu Jun?

606
00:20:01,894 --> 00:20:03,161
(SOOBIN targets the opening.)

607
00:20:03,161 --> 00:20:04,228
Okay.

608
00:20:04,228 --> 00:20:05,228
(He fails.)

609
00:20:05,228 --> 00:20:06,294
What a sharp boy.

610
00:20:06,294 --> 00:20:07,428
Yu Jun!

611
00:20:07,428 --> 00:20:09,494
(Will they be able to brush his teeth?)

612
00:20:09,494 --> 00:20:10,728
Teddy bear!

613
00:20:10,728 --> 00:20:11,928
Yu Jun, teddy bear!

614
00:20:13,194 --> 00:20:15,094
Yu Jun, we have strawberries!

615
00:20:15,094 --> 00:20:16,461
(HUENINGKAI brought strawberries
as their ultimate weapon.)

616
00:20:16,461 --> 00:20:17,961
- Now.
- Let's go.

617
00:20:17,961 --> 00:20:20,994
(Yu Jun got up when he heard
about strawberries.)

618
00:20:20,994 --> 00:20:22,061
It looks delicious!

619
00:20:22,361 --> 00:20:24,461
(Is he heading to the toothbrush,
not strawberries?)

620
00:20:25,661 --> 00:20:26,661
You should have been faster.

621
00:20:27,294 --> 00:20:29,728
(BABY SEA SQUIRTS BY TOGETHER)

622
00:20:30,194 --> 00:20:31,961
(First attempt
at brushing his teeth fails.)

623
00:20:31,961 --> 00:20:33,961
(They don't give up
and try for the second time.)

624
00:20:33,961 --> 00:20:35,761
(Taking a bite of a strawberry)

625
00:20:36,061 --> 00:20:37,194
So tasty!

626
00:20:37,694 --> 00:20:38,617
Delicious!

627
00:20:38,618 --> 00:20:39,728
(Successfully bites the toothbrush!)

628
00:20:40,528 --> 00:20:42,428
(Is this really a strawberry?)

629
00:20:42,428 --> 00:20:44,228
(Let me eat it and find out.)

630
00:20:44,228 --> 00:20:45,228
You're doing great!

631
00:20:45,228 --> 00:20:46,661
(Yu Jun can't know it's a toothbrush.)

632
00:20:46,661 --> 00:20:48,461
You're so good at brushing teeth, Yu Jun.

633
00:20:48,461 --> 00:20:49,928
(Still, they get to brush twice.)

634
00:20:49,928 --> 00:20:51,028
Just ten seconds, Yu Jun.

635
00:20:51,328 --> 00:20:52,961
We made some progress, though.

636
00:20:54,494 --> 00:20:55,961
- You want to do it again?
- Wow!

637
00:20:55,961 --> 00:20:57,994
(Yu Jun opens his mouth by himself
after the strawberry trick.)

638
00:20:57,994 --> 00:20:59,128
You want it again!

639
00:20:59,128 --> 00:21:00,328
Delicious!

640
00:21:00,328 --> 00:21:01,928
- Good boy.
- You're so well-behaved.

641
00:21:02,294 --> 00:21:03,394
(Proud of Yu Jun)

642
00:21:03,394 --> 00:21:04,394
- One more time?
- That's enough.

643
00:21:04,394 --> 00:21:05,494
I guess he likes the taste.

644
00:21:06,494 --> 00:21:08,594
(Looking at Yu Jun's front teeth up close)

645
00:21:08,594 --> 00:21:09,628
(He's on his feet.)

646
00:21:09,628 --> 00:21:11,561
- Yu Jun, you're so good.
- One more time?

647
00:21:11,561 --> 00:21:12,994
- Strawberry!
- It's a strawberry.

648
00:21:12,994 --> 00:21:14,028
- Yu Jun, look.
- Strawberry.

649
00:21:14,028 --> 00:21:16,094
- What's this?
- That looks tasty.

650
00:21:16,094 --> 00:21:17,128
(Mouth open for a strawberry)

651
00:21:17,128 --> 00:21:19,194
Let's eat some snacks.

652
00:21:21,094 --> 00:21:24,128
(Open his mouth.)

653
00:21:24,128 --> 00:21:25,594
You're doing awesome.

654
00:21:26,294 --> 00:21:28,528
(I'm getting that strawberry.)

655
00:21:28,528 --> 00:21:29,794
- Way to go!
- A delicious strawberry.

656
00:21:29,794 --> 00:21:30,994
(All five are doing different things.)

657
00:21:30,994 --> 00:21:32,461
You're almost done, Yu Jun.

658
00:21:32,461 --> 00:21:34,594
- All finished.
- We're done.

659
00:21:34,594 --> 00:21:36,194
Yu Jun, please. Just five seconds.

660
00:21:36,194 --> 00:21:37,261
Here's a strawberry.

661
00:21:37,261 --> 00:21:39,194
- Okay.
- Okay, we're almost done.

662
00:21:39,194 --> 00:21:40,228
I also brushed his front teeth.

663
00:21:41,261 --> 00:21:42,761
In 1, 2, 3.

664
00:21:42,761 --> 00:21:44,128
(Open it again.)

665
00:21:49,094 --> 00:21:50,361
- All right.
- It's okay.

666
00:21:50,361 --> 00:21:52,394
(We're down to just his lower teeth.)

667
00:21:52,861 --> 00:21:54,994
You don't like us
being too forceful, Yu Jun.

668
00:21:55,728 --> 00:21:57,561
You want it slow, right?

669
00:21:58,628 --> 00:22:00,161
Okay. He softened up.

670
00:22:00,161 --> 00:22:02,161
(Yu Jun opened his mouth,
not his heart, for the last time.)

671
00:22:02,161 --> 00:22:05,161
- There!
- Yes. There you go.

672
00:22:05,161 --> 00:22:06,194
Thank you.

673
00:22:06,761 --> 00:22:07,761
There.

674
00:22:07,761 --> 00:22:09,528
- All done!
- We're done!

675
00:22:09,528 --> 00:22:11,961
- Brushing complete!
- Great work!

676
00:22:11,961 --> 00:22:13,328
- Clap your hands, Yu Jun.

677
00:22:13,328 --> 00:22:15,161
All done brushing!

678
00:22:15,161 --> 00:22:17,494
- You're great at brushing your teeth.
- All finished!

679
00:22:17,494 --> 00:22:19,094
- Good job.
- Nice work.

680
00:22:19,094 --> 00:22:20,594
Teeth brushing complete!

681
00:22:22,028 --> 00:22:23,128
Yes, that's it.

682
00:22:24,261 --> 00:22:25,694
This was the toughest one.

683
00:22:25,694 --> 00:22:29,261
(Parenting fact: Nothing is easy.)

684
00:22:30,094 --> 00:22:31,261
- You're here!
- You're happy!

685
00:22:31,261 --> 00:22:33,461
(Time for Yu Jun's cuteness)

686
00:22:33,461 --> 00:22:34,694
Are you here to hug everyone?

687
00:22:35,594 --> 00:22:36,594
Gosh!

688
00:22:37,828 --> 00:22:38,828
I'm jealous.

689
00:22:38,928 --> 00:22:40,661
Yu Jun, what about me?

690
00:22:41,894 --> 00:22:43,361
(I'll just scoot by here.)

691
00:22:43,361 --> 00:22:44,394
(Disappointed)

692
00:22:44,394 --> 00:22:47,461
You can't keep
treating me poorly like this.

693
00:22:48,061 --> 00:22:49,694
This guy is famous.

694
00:22:49,694 --> 00:22:51,961
- He's popular.
- He's the most famous.

695
00:22:51,961 --> 00:22:53,261
Have you ever been a pro?

696
00:22:54,461 --> 00:22:55,628
Yu Jun!

697
00:22:55,628 --> 00:22:56,568
- Okay.
- Yu Jun.

698
00:22:56,569 --> 00:22:57,794
(A pro's mission to win Yu Jun's heart)

699
00:22:58,728 --> 00:23:02,228
(Making sound effects)

700
00:23:02,494 --> 00:23:03,694
I'm Iron Man.

701
00:23:03,694 --> 00:23:05,061
The sound of snacks
from the vending machine.

702
00:23:05,061 --> 00:23:06,794
(Is that food?)

703
00:23:07,428 --> 00:23:08,694
(Making sound effects)

704
00:23:09,661 --> 00:23:10,661
Yu Jun, over here.
(What is it this time?)

705
00:23:11,661 --> 00:23:14,761
(YEONJUN, the pro,
puts in a lot of effort.)

706
00:23:17,394 --> 00:23:18,528
That's dirty.

707
00:23:18,528 --> 00:23:21,694
(A back begging for attention)

708
00:23:21,894 --> 00:23:23,661
Okay. Do you want one more song?

709
00:23:23,661 --> 00:23:25,061
(A serenade only for Yu Jun)

710
00:23:29,861 --> 00:23:32,061
(Not interested)

711
00:23:34,328 --> 00:23:36,394
Hello, hallelujah.

712
00:23:36,794 --> 00:23:40,861
(Let's get closer next time.)

713
00:23:40,861 --> 00:23:42,894
- Your mom is here!
- Yu Jun, your mom is here.

714
00:23:43,294 --> 00:23:45,861
Gosh. You missed her, didn't you?

715
00:23:45,861 --> 00:23:48,228
I missed your mom too.

716
00:23:48,228 --> 00:23:49,694
(Feeling oddly emotional)

717
00:23:49,694 --> 00:23:51,994
- You're so sad.
- We're sorry.

718
00:23:53,628 --> 00:23:54,628
See you again.
Good night, Yu Jun.

719
00:23:55,628 --> 00:23:56,928
- We can get along next time, right?
- Sure.

720
00:23:56,928 --> 00:23:58,861
Yu Jun, don't cry at night
because you miss me.

721
00:23:58,861 --> 00:23:59,861
Don't do that.

722
00:23:59,861 --> 00:24:01,833
You'll feel a little bad when we're gone.

723
00:24:01,834 --> 00:24:03,561
(Each saying something
because they're sad to see him go.)

724
00:24:04,194 --> 00:24:05,428
Are you sad that you're leaving?

725
00:24:05,728 --> 00:24:06,861
Bye, Yu Jun.

726
00:24:08,528 --> 00:24:09,828
He has a great sense of fashion.

727
00:24:09,828 --> 00:24:10,828
Let's go now.

728
00:24:10,828 --> 00:24:13,128
- Bye.
- Goodbye.

729
00:24:13,328 --> 00:24:14,461
So cute.

730
00:24:14,461 --> 00:24:17,494
- Bye, Yu Jun.
- See you again.

731
00:24:18,694 --> 00:24:20,394
Are you feeling sad? Gosh.

732
00:24:20,994 --> 00:24:22,128
Are you really sad?

733
00:24:22,128 --> 00:24:23,694
(No, I'm following Mom.)

734
00:24:26,828 --> 00:24:28,628
- Your mom is still better, right?
- Bye!

735
00:24:28,628 --> 00:24:30,494
- Have a safe trip home.
- Have a safe trip home.

736
00:24:30,761 --> 00:24:32,561
- Thank you.
- He's adorable.

737
00:24:33,228 --> 00:24:35,128
- Good work. Let's eat.
- Let's eat.

738
00:24:35,828 --> 00:24:38,794
- Let's have some food.
- Let's eat. I'm so hungry.

739
00:24:42,094 --> 00:24:49,894
(The quietest moment today)

740
00:24:51,961 --> 00:24:53,494
Mothers are amazing.

741
00:24:53,494 --> 00:24:55,061
One person doing five people's work?

742
00:24:55,061 --> 00:24:56,794
- That's unbelievable.
- It is.

743
00:24:56,794 --> 00:24:58,094
I don't know why the baby cries,

744
00:24:58,094 --> 00:24:59,794
so I have no idea how to calm him down.

745
00:25:00,128 --> 00:25:01,128
Great work.

746
00:25:01,128 --> 00:25:03,628
(7:50 p.m.,
their first parenting diary ends)

747
00:25:03,628 --> 00:25:05,161
- Good work.
- Good work!

748
00:25:05,161 --> 00:25:06,194
I'll slate.

749
00:25:06,494 --> 00:25:07,728
In 1, 2, 3!

750
00:25:07,994 --> 00:25:09,494
- You're suddenly energetic.
- Exactly.

751
00:25:09,494 --> 00:25:11,261
- Good job.
- Great work.

752
00:25:11,261 --> 00:25:12,694
- You did great.
- Nice work.

753
00:25:12,694 --> 00:25:14,228
- You worked so hard.
- This is so difficult.

754
00:25:14,228 --> 00:25:15,928
- It was your first time.
- Yes, it's not easy.

755
00:25:16,894 --> 00:25:18,628
It wasn't that exhausting,
but it was tough.

756
00:25:20,094 --> 00:25:21,628
So what do we write?

757
00:25:21,861 --> 00:25:23,294
"Day One"...

758
00:25:23,294 --> 00:25:26,294
"We had fun playing"...

759
00:25:26,294 --> 00:25:28,228
(BEOMGYU writes down memories
with Yu Jun in the diary.)

760
00:25:28,228 --> 00:25:29,261
"and he also"...

761
00:25:30,894 --> 00:25:31,928
"ate"...

762
00:25:33,461 --> 00:25:34,594
"his meals well."

763
00:25:35,461 --> 00:25:36,894
"But we failed."

764
00:25:36,894 --> 00:25:40,094
"Is there a trick to help him nap easily?"

765
00:25:40,094 --> 00:25:41,094
Nice.

766
00:25:41,261 --> 00:25:42,328
"Thank you"...

767
00:25:43,861 --> 00:25:46,394
"for trusting us"...

768
00:25:47,828 --> 00:25:49,494
"with your baby."

769
00:25:53,494 --> 00:25:55,228
("We had fun playing,
and he ate his meals well.")

770
00:25:55,228 --> 00:25:57,047
("But we couldn't get him to nap.
Is there a trick for that?")

771
00:25:57,048 --> 00:25:58,628
("It was our first day,
but Yu Jun stayed strong.")

772
00:25:58,628 --> 00:25:59,959
(Thank you for trusting us
with your baby.)
